ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAmendments to Appendices I and II of the Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species of Wild Fauna and Flora
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to accept, on behalf of Canada, that the Amendments to Appendices I and II of the CONVENTION ON INTERNATIONAL TRADE IN ENDANGERED SPECIES OF WILD FAUNA AND FLORA, adopted at Bangkok, from March 3 to 14, 2013, be binding in Canada
